  "title": "Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>We are family Karaoke operator with Five outlets in Singapore, we’re looking for full-time service crew who can work during our operation hours from 7pm to 3am. or  12 - 9 pm </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES AND DUTIES</strong><br>\nAs a Service Crew, you will work with your Team Members to deliver a high-quality service experience that exceeds customer expectations:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greeting customers and serving customers</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and housekeeping of work areas</li>\n  <li>Ensure that guests received attention at all times</li>\n  <li>Must be customer service oriented</li>\n  <li>Greeting customers at the door</li>\n  <li>Ensure cleanliness and hygiene of KTV and keeping the environment tidy at all times</li>\n  <li>Able to perform duties like taking food and drink orders, deliver orders, clean room, cashiering and any other ad hoc duties from time to time</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>QUALIFICATIONS AND SKILLS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Secondary level education</li>\n  <li>Outgoing, presentable and service-oriented</li>\n  <li>Cheerful, independent and self-motivated</li>\n  <li>Able to work shifts, weekends and public holiday</li>\n  <li>Candidates with relevant working experience in the Karaoke Or F&amp;B industry</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why join us ?</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Attractive Gross Remuneration</li>\n  <li>Various allowace such as:</li>\n  <li>Transport Allowance</li>\n  <li>Daily Sales Incentive</li>\n  <li>Monthly Commission</li>\n  <li>Full Attendence Incentive</li>\n  <li>13th Month AWS</li>\n  <li>5 Rest Day Per Month</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Welcome Part-Time, rate between $12 - $14/per hour ! (Commiment 24 hours per week)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>",
