    "description": "<p>We welcome you to <strong>K.STAR</strong>, the Singapore Best Themed Karaoke. <strong>K.STAR</strong> is vibrant family friendly karaoke. We look forward to the opportunity to work with you and want you to know that we recognize our employees as our most valuable resource. Our continued success in providing a diversified entertainment platform while elevating and redefining entertainment experience and service to our customers depends on having quality people like yourself and your fellow colleagues. We want you to enjoy your time here and are committed to helping you succeed in your new job. &nbsp;At<strong> K.STAR</strong>, we believe your past values does not represent your future. Every day is a new day with new opportunities to improve and success.</p>",
